{
  "video_id": "UO3N_PRIgX0",
  "title": "The Magic of Making Sound",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 228.0,
      "end_time": 4395.0,
      "text": "(soft whimsical music) (quiet pattering)"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 5893.0,
      "end_time": 7612.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] In Hollywood, everything is magic"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 7612.0,
      "end_time": 8910.0,
      "text": "and make-believe..."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 8910.0,
      "end_time": 11445.0,
      "text": "- [Woman] Gloves with paper clips are dog paws."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 11445.0,
      "end_time": 12692.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] Even what you hear."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 12692.0,
      "end_time": 14817.0,
      "text": "- We are storytellers with sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 14817.0,
      "end_time": 16763.0,
      "text": "Over here we have a feather duster"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 16763.0,
      "end_time": 18960.0,
      "text": "we use for bird-- (feathers fluttering)"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 18960.0,
      "end_time": 19446.0,
      "text": "bird wings."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 19446.0,
      "end_time": 21450.0,
      "text": "We bring sound into the story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 21450.0,
      "end_time": 25329.0,
      "text": "and we can create any mood with that sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 25329.0,
      "end_time": 27129.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] When you watch a film,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 27129.0,
      "end_time": 29900.0,
      "text": "much of what you&#39;re hearing was created..."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 29900.0,
      "end_time": 30669.0,
      "text": "(feet tromping heavily)"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 30669.0,
      "end_time": 33257.0,
      "text": "From footsteps on a snowy path"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 33257.0,
      "end_time": 34469.0,
      "text": "to a vicious thunderstorm."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 34469.0,
      "end_time": 35427.0,
      "text": "(leaves rustling)"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 35427.0,
      "end_time": 36514.0,
      "text": "(thunder booming)"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 36514.0,
      "end_time": 39972.0,
      "text": "- [Woman] Weather is a really interesting thing to recreate."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 39972.0,
      "end_time": 41510.0,
      "text": "- They make it exciting. (chuckles)"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 41510.0,
      "end_time": 44221.0,
      "text": "- [Woman] It depends on the elements that we&#39;re using,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 44221.0,
      "end_time": 46559.0,
      "text": "and how it&#39;s filmed, and what they wanna hear."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 46560.0,
      "end_time": 48178.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] Here at the Warner Brothers&#39; lot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 48178.0,
      "end_time": 50598.0,
      "text": "Foley artists practice their craft;"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 50598.0,
      "end_time": 52527.0,
      "text": "and if they do their jobs right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 52527.0,
      "end_time": 54157.0,
      "text": "you won&#39;t even notice."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 54157.0,
      "end_time": 56656.0,
      "text": "- [Woman] People take sound for granted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 56656.0,
      "end_time": 58988.0,
      "text": "but you would miss it if it wasn&#39;t there."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 58988.0,
      "end_time": 61655.0,
      "text": "(bag crunching)"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 63199.0,
      "end_time": 66256.0,
      "text": "(pensive music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 66256.0,
      "end_time": 69250.0,
      "text": "(cloth fluttering) - Foley is the art of sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 69250.0,
      "end_time": 73417.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s creating sounds in sync with what&#39;s happening onscreen."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 74706.0,
      "end_time": 78260.0,
      "text": "The art of Foley goes back to the old radio days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 78260.0,
      "end_time": 80383.0,
      "text": "where you would see the sound guys"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 80383.0,
      "end_time": 82429.0,
      "text": "with their clomping with their coconuts."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 82430.0,
      "end_time": 84222.0,
      "text": "This is what we use for horse hooves."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 84222.0,
      "end_time": 87590.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re plungers, and we stuff them"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 87590.0,
      "end_time": 89848.0,
      "text": "with cloth and a little tape;"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 89848.0,
      "end_time": 90811.0,
      "text": "and here we go."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 90811.0,
      "end_time": 93443.0,
      "text": "(muffled clopping)"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 93443.0,
      "end_time": 95237.0,
      "text": "Jack Foley came in and he thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 95237.0,
      "end_time": 99154.0,
      "text": "\"If I do those sounds in sync with the picture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 99991.0,
      "end_time": 102405.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;ve just taken a whole step out.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 102405.0,
      "end_time": 103949.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] Jack Foley&#39;s legacy in sound"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 103949.0,
      "end_time": 107957.0,
      "text": "began in the 1920s, as talkies swept Hollywood."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 107957.0,
      "end_time": 110916.0,
      "text": "Ever since, the reproduction of sound effects"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 110916.0,
      "end_time": 113374.0,
      "text": "added to film in post-production"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 113374.0,
      "end_time": 115702.0,
      "text": "is called the art of Foley."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 115703.0,
      "end_time": 118632.0,
      "text": "- The Foley stage consists of different surfaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 118632.0,
      "end_time": 120925.0,
      "text": "- This is walking on leaves, or in a forest."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 120925.0,
      "end_time": 122298.0,
      "text": "(shoes clomping)"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 122298.0,
      "end_time": 125631.0,
      "text": "(hissing and pattering)"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 126810.0,
      "end_time": 131183.0,
      "text": "For snow, what we normally use is regular play sand."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 131183.0,
      "end_time": 133272.0,
      "text": "And then to add to that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 133272.0,
      "end_time": 136105.0,
      "text": "sometimes you hear that familiar crunch..."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 136105.0,
      "end_time": 139606.0,
      "text": "Which, we use cornstarch. (bag crunches)"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 139606.0,
      "end_time": 143236.0,
      "text": "Your ear hears snow; but in actuality, it&#39;s sand."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 143236.0,
      "end_time": 146153.0,
      "text": "(footsteps crunch)"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 149622.0,
      "end_time": 152000.0,
      "text": "(solemn music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 152000.0,
      "end_time": 154114.0,
      "text": "- It&#39;s almost like a prop house."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 154114.0,
      "end_time": 156749.0,
      "text": "We have collected different things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 156749.0,
      "end_time": 159176.0,
      "text": "because everything here should make a sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 159176.0,
      "end_time": 162580.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a classic squeaky hinge. (metal squeaks)"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 162580.0,
      "end_time": 166505.0,
      "text": "Pinecones can be used for cracking ice. (faint crackling)"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 166505.0,
      "end_time": 169353.0,
      "text": "- You have the three people that are on the stage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 169354.0,
      "end_time": 171955.0,
      "text": "the mixer and the two Foley artists, which--"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 171955.0,
      "end_time": 175905.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s important that you have a team that&#39;s cohesive."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 175905.0,
      "end_time": 177433.0,
      "text": "- [Red Shirt] Y&#39;know, somethin&#39;s cracking, popping."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 177433.0,
      "end_time": 178957.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know what it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 178957.0,
      "end_time": 181196.0,
      "text": "- [Man] Is it this? (leaves rustling)"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 181196.0,
      "end_time": 183952.0,
      "text": "Sometimes it takes a little trial and error"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 183952.0,
      "end_time": 185637.0,
      "text": "to see what works best."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 185637.0,
      "end_time": 186470.0,
      "text": "Hold on."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 186470.0,
      "end_time": 189573.0,
      "text": "- We have a streamer that goes across the screen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 189573.0,
      "end_time": 191997.0,
      "text": "and when the streamer gets to the end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 191997.0,
      "end_time": 195300.0,
      "text": "that tells us when that sound should start."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 195300.0,
      "end_time": 197131.0,
      "text": "(rustling)"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 197132.0,
      "end_time": 199228.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an interesting dance."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 199228.0,
      "end_time": 200803.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s really nothing"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 200803.0,
      "end_time": 204136.0,
      "text": "that we can&#39;t do here, imagination-wise."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 205671.0,
      "end_time": 207593.0,
      "text": "- Right now, we&#39;re in the control room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 207593.0,
      "end_time": 208809.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s where I mix;"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 208809.0,
      "end_time": 213376.0,
      "text": "and I listen to them performing to the picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 213376.0,
      "end_time": 215307.0,
      "text": "I try not to look at them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 215307.0,
      "end_time": 217178.0,
      "text": "because I really don&#39;t wanna see what they&#39;re using."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 217178.0,
      "end_time": 219113.0,
      "text": "I wanna see how it sounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 219113.0,
      "end_time": 221951.0,
      "text": "(playful music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 221951.0,
      "end_time": 224868.0,
      "text": "(thunder crackles)"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 225990.0,
      "end_time": 229914.0,
      "text": "- All sound is two elements hitting one another."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 229914.0,
      "end_time": 232458.0,
      "text": "- With rain, if it&#39;s hitting a puddle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 232459.0,
      "end_time": 234830.0,
      "text": "or if it&#39;s hitting someone&#39;s face,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 234830.0,
      "end_time": 237709.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s all gonna sound different;"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 237709.0,
      "end_time": 240215.0,
      "text": "so those are very specific little things"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 240215.0,
      "end_time": 243480.0,
      "text": "that we have to watch and look at."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 244210.0,
      "end_time": 244974.0,
      "text": "Okay, Mary Jo."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 244974.0,
      "end_time": 247423.0,
      "text": "- [Mary Jo] Here we go."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 247423.0,
      "end_time": 250340.0,
      "text": "(liquid pattering)"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 257188.0,
      "end_time": 260521.0,
      "text": "(high-pitched chirping)"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 262787.0,
      "end_time": 265650.0,
      "text": "(distant thunder)"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 265650.0,
      "end_time": 266776.0,
      "text": "- Wind is interesting because"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 266776.0,
      "end_time": 269861.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s usually what the wind is blowing through."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 269861.0,
      "end_time": 273789.0,
      "text": "- Alice is gonna use the Batman cape to create the sails,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 273789.0,
      "end_time": 275654.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m going to create the boat"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 275654.0,
      "end_time": 277745.0,
      "text": "actually going through the water."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 277745.0,
      "end_time": 278995.0,
      "text": "Okay, let&#39;s go."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 280549.0,
      "end_time": 284798.0,
      "text": "(fabric fluttering) (water splashing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 284798.0,
      "end_time": 288473.0,
      "text": "- If we&#39;re doing a boat going through waves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 288473.0,
      "end_time": 290437.0,
      "text": "we would use the big tub that we have"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 290437.0,
      "end_time": 292687.0,
      "text": "to get that slapping sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 293771.0,
      "end_time": 297938.0,
      "text": "or churning up the water a lot in the tub with our hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 299108.0,
      "end_time": 300531.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a lot of sound, like--"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 300531.0,
      "end_time": 303826.0,
      "text": "Like a lot of things artistic, is very subjective;"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 303826.0,
      "end_time": 306858.0,
      "text": "so, I have to make that judgment call."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 306858.0,
      "end_time": 310690.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a great moment when you get the perfect sound;"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 310690.0,
      "end_time": 312488.0,
      "text": "and they don&#39;t always know it, but I do."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 312488.0,
      "end_time": 313620.0,
      "text": "- How was that, Mary Jo?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 313620.0,
      "end_time": 314741.0,
      "text": "- [Mary Jo] Sounded great."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 314741.0,
      "end_time": 317712.0,
      "text": "- When there are multiple weather elements involved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 317712.0,
      "end_time": 321503.0,
      "text": "we might do all the specific things first,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 321504.0,
      "end_time": 324626.0,
      "text": "and then go back and do maybe a general sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 324626.0,
      "end_time": 328965.0,
      "text": "We have a shot here of a hiker coming down the waterfall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 328965.0,
      "end_time": 333181.0,
      "text": "so I&#39;m doing the sound of the carabiner and his rope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 333182.0,
      "end_time": 337349.0,
      "text": "and his equipment. (metal squeaks)"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 340484.0,
      "end_time": 341317.0,
      "text": "How was that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 341317.0,
      "end_time": 342150.0,
      "text": "- [Mary Jo] That was cool."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 342150.0,
      "end_time": 342983.0,
      "text": "- Great."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 342983.0,
      "end_time": 345733.0,
      "text": "(water sloshing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 346731.0,
      "end_time": 349731.0,
      "text": "(water splattering)"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 351250.0,
      "end_time": 352991.0,
      "text": "- So, I&#39;m gonna play it back all together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 352991.0,
      "end_time": 355920.0,
      "text": "and see what we&#39;ve got. (keyboard clacking)"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 355930.0,
      "end_time": 359371.0,
      "text": "(water splashing) (metal squeaking)"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 359371.0,
      "end_time": 361834.0,
      "text": "- We really layer everything"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 361834.0,
      "end_time": 364960.0,
      "text": "so the mixers can mix how they wanna hear it;"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 364960.0,
      "end_time": 369544.0,
      "text": "and we do things also that are a little over the top,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 369544.0,
      "end_time": 373710.0,
      "text": "because we have to fight with music, sometimes dialogue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 375345.0,
      "end_time": 377225.0,
      "text": "but hopefully when you hear it at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
